trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] This attribute should only be used as dependency property option.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]Dette attributtet kan bare brukes som avhengighet egenskapen alternativet.

trans-unit.source: Attributes are ignored if declared on a .NET property.
trans-unit.target: Attributter ignoreres hvis deklarert i en .NET-egenskap.

trans-unit.source: The ValidationOptionAttribute is intended to be used on Meta-properties only.
It will be ignored for instance properties.
For more information, see [Using Activity Properties](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/974353d4-28f9-4202-890d-b36981876148) for more details.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [ved hjelp av aktiviteten Egenskaper](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/974353d4-28f9-4202-890d-b36981876148) for flere detaljer.

trans-unit.source: If the ValidationOptionAttribute is not specified, the behavior defaults to <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.ValidationOption?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis ValidationOptionAttribute ikke er angitt, bruker du virkemåten på <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.ValidationOption?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.ValidationOption?displayProperty=fullName>
